title: [Arles' Outfitting]
[Arles' Combat Gear]
[Arles' Armory]
description: Beneath a modwir beam ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the dark brocade walls.  A iron-bound ebonwood chest and an elegantly carved oak armoire sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on a glossy black ebonwood floor.
